  "title": "Accounts & Admin Executive (1-Year Contract)",
  "description": "<p>[Job ID: 1425393]</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage payments, reimbursements, invoices and maintain accurate financial records.</li><li>Assist in preparing financial reports on expenses, taxes and other data for management review.</li><li>Act as the primary liaison with external auditors and accounting firms.</li><li>Provide administrative support to internal teams and oversee general office operations.</li><li>Manage and track company assets, facilities and related documentation.</li><li>Coordinate vendor-related matters, including contracts and service arrangements.</li><li>Serve as the main point of contact for engagements with government agencies.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 1–2 years of experience in accounting, finance or administrative roles.</li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office Suite, especially Microsoft Excel.</li></ul><p>To Apply, please kindly email your updated resume to cv_estheryip@goodjobcreations.com.sg</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Yip Yan Wen, Esther</p><p>EA Personnel Reg. no.: R25152371</p><p>EA License no.: 07C5771</p>",
